{"tid":125031,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"新手問羽田到新宿交通方法","createTime":"2017-02-18T06:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T08:23:51.000Z","uid":701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d3d5d5cff0fb6966ebe1e903efc516cc8f9525a","tid":125031,"uid":701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:35:09.000Z","msg":"本人成3x歲黎緊三月中先同老婆第一次去去東京，我地座香港快運成朝早五點到羽田機場，上網睇過話座京急線去品川站，再轉山手線去新宿就到，但又見可以座利木津巴士去新宿，其實邊樣慳時間同直接到呢？ <br />\n我地訂左住新宿apa, 近大久保公園個面，請大家指教預弟，同埋座巴士係咪總站就係新宿呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e7bb9132ce43e529d83de357b19a00a4f379ee","tid":125031,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:46:34.000Z","msg":"巴士就方便d 日本好多時轉車要行上行落又冇扶手電梯<br />\n<br />\n但你間酒店邊個站都要行10分鐘路程先到 夜晚仲要周圍都係牛郎店同夜總會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607efafcdab19dd132209766f11794a563587963","tid":125031,"uid":701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T07:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴士就方便d 日本好多時轉車要行上行落又冇扶手電梯<br />\n<br />\n但你間酒店邊個站都要行10分鐘路程先到 夜晚仲要周圍都係牛郎店同夜總會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係訂左呢個apa呀<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/150918_6e387c34c1360bffa9651c98eb4172b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F150918_6e387c34c1360bffa9651c98eb4172b2.jpg&h=88e4d25d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76c5040d97e4dbc2b17b689e8f23e7de2ff8836f","tid":125031,"uid":64481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T07:40:09.000Z","msg":"Book正人中龍果間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b726d7d504b774c85e9a47bfe44f06d0aca5195","tid":125031,"uid":18650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/153156_2b6ad54fab9f5fdcbda0c9ecab6af89c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F153156_2b6ad54fab9f5fdcbda0c9ecab6af89c.jpg&h=54191441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔識路最好搭電車啦（搭的士仲好），巴士落錯站你仲慘<br />\n<br />\n官網其實都有講點去<br />\nJR「新宿駅」（東口）徒歩6分　<br />\n<br />\n到左新宿站向東口行，出左去之後開住google map跟住行實無死"},{"pid":"868dff72cd951f17a7e08cbd523b7d23c20004b6","tid":125031,"uid":701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:23:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/153156_2b6ad54fab9f5fdcbda0c9ecab6af89c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F153156_2b6ad54fab9f5fdcbda0c9ecab6af89c.jpg&h=54191441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔識路最好搭電車啦（搭的士仲好），巴士落錯站你仲慘<br />\n<br />\n官網其實都有講點去<br />\nJR「新宿駅」（東口）徒歩6分　<br />\n<br />\n到左新宿站向東口行，出左去之後開住google map跟住行實無死</blockquote><br />\n多謝你既資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}